The <b>ChuoSeiki QT-series controller</b> connect to PC via an RS232 interface. It does not require any special driver to run. However, if you connect the controller via a device such as a USB-RS232 converter, be sure to install its driver.

To download the QT-series controller's user manual, please follow this link [http://www.chuo.co.jp/english/contents/hp0063/list.php?CNo=63], select the correct controller and download the manual under the <i>Product information</i> bar. 

